This is the Android 'ToDo List Widget' application

HISTORY
This app was released on the market in June 2010. 
In December 2010 I released the code as open source under the GPL v3.0 license
More information about the published app can be found at <http://chris.bailey.name>
See the CHANGELOG file for complete version history

DEVELOPERS
For developers, you'll need the Android SDK, Eclipse and the ADT plugin.
Information about obtaining these can be found at:
<http://developer.android.com/sdk/installing.html>

